**** wpa_supplicant ****

** Simple config for an open network **
network={
  ssid="hotel_wifi"
  scan_ssid=1
}

** Simple config for a WPA or WPA-PSK network **
network={
  ssid="home_network"
  scan_ssid=1
  psk="correct battery horse staple"
  key_mgmt=WPA-PSK
}

$sudo wpa_supplicant -i wlan0 -c wifi-client.conf
$sudo dhclient wlan0
